      • setCollapseToLast

        public void setCollapseToLast(boolean collapseToLast)
        If set to true, timestamp-collapsing writes out the last best capture in the collapse group, instead of the first.

        Initial value is false.

        Parameters:
        collapseToLast - the collapseToLast to set
        See Also:
        DupeTimestampLastBestStatusFilter

      • findLastCapture

        public org.archive.format.cdx.CDXLine findLastCapture(String url,
                                                      String digest,
                                                      boolean ignoreRobots)
        Look up the latest (non-revisit) capture of url in the CDX database. If digest is non-null, return only a capture with identical digest.
        Parameters:
        url - URL (in regular form) to look for
        digest - content digest in the same format as CDX database, or null if any version qualifies.
        ignoreRobots - whether robots.txt-excluded captures qualify
        Returns:
        CDXLine found
